title: Brand New Luxury In Dallas! Granite, Wood Floors, Washer/Drye Incl!!!!
posting_body: Brand new midrise  in a prime location, modern amenities and luxury finishes.
Located only minutes by car from the center of Downtown, Uptown, Deep Ellum and Oak Lawn, just to name a few of the popular destinations at your fingertips.
Located just off Highway 75 provides access to all of DFW by car.
Just a 5-minute walk from the Walnut Hill DART Station, which provides easy access to Downtown as well as the rest of the DART network, including the DFW airport  .
Walking distance to dining and entertainment.
Close proximity to Whole Foods, Trader Joes and Sprouts.
Th apartment homes are well designed and attention to detail is evident.
Our kitchens offer deep stainless-steel sinks, granite counter tops, modern lighting, custom cabinets and a stylish tile backsplash.

Your new home doesn't stop at your door, Modena offers a full suite of community amenities for our residents: a dog walking area and pet cleaning station, resort style pool with tanning ledge, a modern fitness center, outdoor grilling station, billiards and even electric car charging stations!
